                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Merry</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Managua</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1899-02-26">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 26, 1899</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The revolution in Nicaragua appears to be a failure; demanding the position of
                    strict neutrality our citizens.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Merry.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
